ril 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said regarding the major sins, \u201cThey are associating partners with Allah, disrespect to parents, killing someone, and false testimony.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5977, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 88 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/major-sins-idolatry-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":32182,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Major sins are idolatry, infanticide, adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the greatest sin?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo set up a partner alongside Allah, even though He alone created you.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo kill your child, fearing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32841,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/three-worst-major-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":32182,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Three of the worst major